General Information
===================

BDSIM version 0.91, Geant4 toolkit for radiation transport in accelerators

The official web site is:
	http://www.pp.rhul.ac.uk/bdsim

The official Geant4 web site is:
	http://geant4.web.cern.ch

Written by G.A. Blair

Currently maintained and developed by
